The paper deals with a system for estimating the reachability and performance of online advertising campaigns, which involves processing and analyzing large amounts of data in real-time. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Information Retrieval (cs.IR) for the search and retrieval of relevant data, Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) for the efficient processing of large datasets, Databases (cs.DB) for the storage and retrieval of data, Machine Learning (cs.LG) for the development of predictive models, and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) for the analysis of online user behavior.
